reviewText: I love Kenny Rogers. Saw a Christmas concert downtown locally.loved that..I thought it was cool how,they brought 5 kids from different backgrounds. .also love Garth Brooks and Boyz to men..average dvd special. .I was tearing up at the beginning when he 1st met the kids:)

I was very disappointed with this dvd It is very short and poor value for money
The children are very ordinary and there is really only one song on the DVD

Trevor B
This is not a Christmas Special, only a lot of before Special, kids are great but still not a Christmas Special.
I wished he had sung more songs.
Good music and great for the holidays!  Anyone that enjoys Kenny will like this DVD Takes you home for the holidays
